      "@id": "ko:article/themarco-retrozone",
      "@type": "ko:Article",
      "title": "RetroZone - A cool display engine for web games that looks authentically retro, both CRT and vector displays",
      "url": "https://github.com/TheMarco/retrozone",
      "publishedDate": "2026-03-21",
      "readDate": "2026-03-23",
      "language": "en",
      "abstract": "Moteur d'affichage rétro pour jeux HTML5 avec effets CRT et vector authentiques via WebGL shaders. Zéro dépendance, fonctionne avec n'importe quel canvas.",
      "hasAuthor": "ko:author/themarco",
